}  OR  {
    "status": "publish",
    "topic": ["car", "auto"],
    "title": "Tesla is the best car right now"
}  Success Response  Code  :  200 OK    Content example  {
    "news": {
        "id": 25,
        "topic": "car",
        "status": "publish",
        "title": "Updated, Tesla New Car Released this Month"
    }
}  Error Response  Condition  : If Token is Expired.  Code  :  401 UNAUTHORIZED  Content  :  {
